Steve VanMatre is with Coaches Cantu and 8 others.
September 4 at 12:04 PM ·

Premont ISD:

1. Ended 2019-2020 school year with $705,990 budget surplus;
2. 21% Enrollment Gain since 2018;
3. Recognized by Texas Education Agency as Fast Growth District;
4. 95% of Premont Collegiate students enrolled in college earning courses at TAMU-K, Del Mar and Coastal Bend College;
5. Recognized Academic performance on STAAR tests;
6. Superior Financial Rating on TEA Financial Rating System;
7. Recognized by Gov. Abbott in 2019 State of the State address as one of top five districts for college and career readiness;
8. $0.20 tax reduction since 2018;
9. $14M investment in facilities;
10. National news on CNN, PBS, Texas Tribune, Edutopia and EdSource
11. 2019 Region 2 School Board of the Year

#flagshipdistrict

