shared_text:
Steve VanMatre
September 8, 2019 at 10:39 AM ·

Did you know? Blessed by funding and support of the Texas Education Agency and strong partnerships with Brooks County ISD, Freer ISD, Coastal Bend College, ESC-2, and Texas A&M University-Kingsville:
#. 65% of PCHS students attend classes on the campus of TAMU-K;
#. 21% of PCHS students attend construction/welding courses at Falfurrias HS through CBC;
#. 35% of PCHS students attend STEM Engineering/Biology courses at the STEM Center through TAMUK and Project Lead the Way;
#. 23% of PCHS students attend Medical Academy courses at Freer HS through CBC.

Endless Opportunities....Exceptional Outcomes!
#flagshipdistrict

